\c 5
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukuvikelwa ezitheni
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. NgeNehilothi. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Beka indlebe emazwini ami, N\nd kosi\nd*; unanzelele ukububula kwami\x + Hlab. 39.3.\x*.
\v 2 Lalela ilizwi lokukhala kwami, Nkosi yami loNkulunkulu wami\x + Hlab. 84.3.\x*; ngoba ngikhuleka kuwe\x + Hlab. 65.2.\x*.
\v 3 N\nd kosi\nd*, ekuseni uzalizwa ilizwi lami\x + Hlab. 30.5. 88.13. 90.14. 130.6. 143.8. Hlab. 46.5. 119.147.\x*; ekuseni ngizahlela \add umkhuleko wami\add* ngakuwe\x + Jobe 33.5. Hlab. 50.21.\x*, ngilinde\x + Mika 7.7.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba kawusuye uNkulunkulu othokoza ebubini; omubi kayikuhlala lawe.
\v 5 Abazikhukhumezayo kabayikuma phambi kwamehlo akho; uzonda bonke abenzi bobubi\x + Hlab. 73.3. 75.4. Hab. 1.13.\x*.
\v 6 Uzababhubhisa abaqamba amanga. IN\nd kosi\nd* iyamenyanya umuntu wegazi lenkohliso\x + Hlab. 4.2. Isam. 21.8. 22.15.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa mina, ngizangena endlini yakho ngobukhulu besihawu sakho, ngikhothame\x + Hlab. 132.7.\x* ngikhangele ethempelini lakho elingcwele, ngokukwesaba\x + 1 Kho. 8.29,30. Hlab. 132.7.\x*.
\v 8 N\nd kosi\nd*, ngikhokhelele ekulungeni kwakho ngenxa yezitha zami\x + Hlab. 23.3. 25.4.\x*, wenze indlela yakho iqonde phambi kwami\x + Ezra 8.21.\x*.
\v 9 Ngoba kalikho iqiniso emlonyeni wazo, ingaphakathi yazo izinkohlakalo\x + Hlab. 49.11.\x*; umphimbo wazo\x + Roma 3.13.\x* ulingcwaba elivulekileyo\x + Jer. 5.16.\x*, zibamba amehlo ngolimi lwazo\x + Zaga 2.16. 7.5. Hlab. 12.2. Hlab. 36.2.\x*.
\v 10 Tshono uthi zilecala, Nkulunkulu, kaziwe ngamacebo azo; uzilahle ngenxa yobunengi beziphambeko zazo, ngoba zikuvukele.
\v 11 Kodwa kabathabe\x + Isa. 65.13.\x* bonke abathembela kuwe\x + Hlab. 2.12.\x*, bamemeze kokuphela ngentokozo, ngoba ubavikele; lalabo abathanda ibizo lakho kabajabule kuwe\x + 1 Sam. 2.1. Hlab. 9.2.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba wena N\nd kosi\nd*, uzabusisa olungileyo, uzamhanqa ngomusa njengesihlangu esikhulu\x + Hlab. 35.2.\x*.
